{"tid":1295901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉將於下午四時見記者","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:09:42.000Z","uid":267881,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"33980f907c91c27e84106be9bf8d6b96228218ce","tid":1295901,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/349407/逃犯條例-葉劉四時見記者-田少再抽水-留名等睇葉劉賴死\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F349407%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E5%9B%9B%E6%99%82%E8%A6%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E7%94%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%BD%E6%B0%B4-%E7%95%99%E5%90%8D%E7%AD%89%E7%9D%87%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%E8%B3%B4%E6%AD%BB&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5d9d82b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/349407/逃犯條例-葉劉四時見記者-田少再抽水-留名等睇葉劉賴死</a><br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊今天（8日）要求黨主席張宇人辭去行會成員一職，同時認為新民黨主席葉劉淑儀和資深大律師湯家驊亦需辭任行會，葉劉將於下午四時見記者回應。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊下午2時在facebook發文，指自由黨應代表市民，真實向政府反映意見，不應「幫政府站在市民的對立面」，又認為改组行政會議，應由黨主席張宇人辭任行會成員做起。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊又點名葉劉需為《逃犯條例》修訂爭議問責，辭去行會成員一職。葉劉將於下午四時在新民黨總部召開記者會回應事件，田北俊則「先下手為強」，直言：「留名等睇葉劉賴死，兼利用我今日嘅言論去鞏固自己的支持者。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1263df5530be1c634dbec460e9d2b5404e03a7","tid":1295901,"uid":35342,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"儀姐姐今次又要插蛾妹妹幾多刀呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090c7c5610c0aa6f6b71e735c5acb6e7dcf5c91c","tid":1295901,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"仲有五分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51da6cc2cea212415a241a82f9149bc8137a61b2","tid":1295901,"uid":38548,"like":5,"dislike":